00:10:21,517 --> 00:10:24,390
"I'm not in a position
to do this," you will be.

263
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:27,210
There are two main approaches
you can take at this stage.

264
00:10:27,210 --> 00:10:28,650
Let me explain them both.

265
00:10:28,650 --> 00:10:32,070
First, diversification,
spreading your investments

266
00:10:32,070 --> 00:10:35,130
across multiple asset classes
to protect your wealth

267
00:10:35,130 --> 00:10:36,690
and reduce risk.

268
00:10:36,690 --> 00:10:39,300
Second, high-conviction plays,

269
00:10:39,300 --> 00:10:42,150
concentrating your resources
on a few investments

270
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:44,280
that you have a deep understanding of

271
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:45,870
and strong confidence in.

272
00:10:45,870 --> 00:10:47,580
This approach carries more risks,

273
00:10:47,580 --> 00:10:51,990
but can lead to faster and
larger returns if executed well.

274
00:10:51,990 --> 00:10:55,230
Many billionaires, including
Elon Musk and Jeff Bezos,

275
00:10:55,230 --> 00:10:56,070
built their wealth

276
00:10:56,070 --> 00:10:59,070
by focusing a high-conviction
place like these.

277
00:10:59,070 --> 00:11:00,210
The approach you choose

278
00:11:00,210 --> 00:11:02,820
depends on your risk
tolerance and expertise.

279
00:11:02,820 --> 00:11:04,119
If you are just starting,

280
00:11:04,119 --> 00:11:07,050
diversification might
be the smarter route.

281
00:11:07,050 --> 00:11:09,960
However, as you gain
experience and confidence,

282
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,850
high-conviction plays can help you

283
00:11:11,850 --> 00:11:13,860
expand your wealth even further.

284
00:11:13,860 --> 00:11:15,720
Remember, the goal at this stage

285
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:18,510
is to acquire assets that work for you.

286
00:11:18,510 --> 00:11:20,910
Every dollar you invest
should have a purpose

287
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:22,050
to grow your wealth

288
00:11:22,050 --> 00:11:24,693
and to move you closer
to financial freedom.

289
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:31,680
Welcome to the final stage, mastery.

290
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:33,930
This is where you've
achieved financial freedom

291
00:11:33,930 --> 00:11:36,030
and can live life on your own terms.

292
00:11:36,030 --> 00:11:38,910
At this level, money
is no longer a concern.

293
00:11:38,910 --> 00:11:42,270
Your assets generate enough
income to cover your expenses,

294
00:11:42,270 --> 00:11:43,500
fund your lifestyle,

295
00:11:43,500 --> 00:11:46,050
and allow you to focus
on what truly matters.

296
00:11:46,050 --> 00:11:48,180
But mastery isn't just about enjoying

297
00:11:48,180 --> 00:11:50,970
the fruits of your labor
on a beach in the Maldives.

298
00:11:50,970 --> 00:11:52,601
It's also about leaving a legacy

299
00:11:52,601 --> 00:11:55,013
and helping others
achieve their own success.

300
00:11:55,013 --> 00:11:56,970
The wealthiest people in the world,

301
00:11:56,970 --> 00:11:59,310
from Warren Buffett to Oprah Winfrey,

302
00:11:59,310 --> 00:12:01,590
understand the importance of giving back

303
00:12:01,590 --> 00:12:04,292
and building something that
lasts beyond their lifetime.

304
00:12:04,292 --> 00:12:06,870
At this stage, your focus should shift

305
00:12:06,870 --> 00:12:10,350
from accumulating wealth to
managing and preserving it.

306
00:12:10,350 --> 00:12:13,380
This means reinvesting
profits that maintain

307
00:12:13,380 --> 00:12:16,230
and grow your portfolio, mentoring others,

308
00:12:16,230 --> 00:12:18,690
and sharing the lessons
you've learned along the way.

309
00:12:18,690 --> 00:12:22,260
Ultimately, mastery is
about more than just money.

310
00:12:22,260 --> 00:12:24,540
It's about achieving true freedom;

311
00:12:24,540 --> 00:12:26,790
freedom to spend your time as you wish,

312
00:12:26,790 --> 00:12:28,890
freedom to pursue your passions,

313
00:12:28,890 --> 00:12:32,250
and freedom to create a lasting
legacy that benefits others.

314
00:12:32,250 --> 00:12:35,250
So are you ready to
follow this path to wealth

315
00:12:35,250 --> 00:12:38,070
and take control of your financial future?

316
00:12:38,070 --> 00:12:39,780
The journey won't be easy,

317
00:12:39,780 --> 00:12:41,580
but if you follow these stages,

318
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:44,040
you'll unlock the life
you've always dreamed of

319
